sections.heading: High Impact Economic Futures Act, how cited
sections.text: Sections 77-3113 to 77-3120 shall be known and may be cited as the Creating High Impact Economic Futures Act and may also be referred to as the CHIEF Act.SourceLaws 1984, LB 372, ยง 1;R.S.1943, (2022), ยง 13-201;Laws 2024, LB1344, ยง 1.
